text: Compsosoma vestitipenne is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dmytro Zajciw in 1962. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma vestitipenne. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1962
